{
  "stem": "4284.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "We were shoved through a room, a facility-- not a hallway-- it's a very large room that had a, a shower of excruciating solution fall on you.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And it especially hurt the head that had just been shaven, which as it turned out was a disinfection solution.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was a shower, a real shower, and no towels or anything like this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the fore room before you went into the shower, they asked, has anybody been a policeman in the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were some.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were taken apart-- aside, and they were immediately beaten to death.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, we thought that's a punishment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, the camp police, which-- we didn't know where we were at that time-- did not want competition, and so beatings were right in front of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was really one of the earliest times I had seen murders right in front of me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, you saw a lot of dead people and beatings and hangings, but you didn't see blatant murders right in front of you.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were shoved out of the room wet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as we walked out the door, the packages came flying at you, which was nothing more than a bundle of white and blue striped clothing with a pair of clophoppers, which are just wooden shoes-- no socks, no underwear, nothing.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you were told, grab it-- not a question of size or anything.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We're sitting there shivering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was August.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was already cold in the place we were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know yet where we were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as we walked out to this place after the shower, we walked out into this incredible strange illumination, which came from stacks.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
